Package: gettext
Version: 0.10.35
Revision: 4
Source: gnu
Essential: yes
Depends: base-files
UpdateConfigGuess: true
UpdateLibtool: true
SetCPPFLAGS: -traditional-cpp
Patch: %f.patch
ConfigureParams: --infodir=%p/share/info --with-included-gettext
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
Description: Localization support
DescDetail: <<
The gettext package provides the i18n and l10n support used by many
GNU programs but missing from the system C library.
<<
DescPort: <<
Uses autoconf. Checks the host type - the usual fix. Uses an evil hack
to actually build and install a shared libintl library and link
against it.
<<
